oai_dc:dc.dc:title: A Day in the Life of a Large Animal Veterinary Technician
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: White, David P.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: veterinary technician
large animal practice
veterinary practice
outside work environment
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A veterinary technician can be an asset to a large animal practice. One benefit to having a large animal technician is that they can help a veterinarian to become more efficient throughout the day. The use of a technician allows the veterinarian to focus more of their time to the technical aspects of veterinary medicine. There are also many advantages to being a large animal technician, which include a variety of duties involving an outside work environment.
